OL,3,CMan arrested nine years after
OL,4,Cnotorious 'Putney Pusher' incident
OL,6,FA man has been arrested by police
OL,7,Fhunting the "Putney Pusher".
OL,9,FThe 44-year-old man has been detained
OL,10,Fnine years after a jogger allegedly
OL,11,Fpushed a woman into the path of an
OL,12,Foncoming bus on Putney Bridge on the
OL,13,F4th May 2017.
OL,15,FPolice released CCTV of the incident
OL,16,Fat the time, which showed a bus swerve
OL,17,Fout of the way after the 33-year-old
OL,18,Fvictim was pushed into the road. She
OL,19,Fescaped with minor injuries.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@[O]
