OL,3,CMan arrested nine years after
OL,4,Cnotorious 'Putney Pusher' incident
OL,6,FBus driver Oliver Salbris managed to
OL,7,Fswerve to avoid running her over,
OL,8,Ftelling the Sunday Times: "If I hadn't
OL,9,Fswerved, I would have smashed her head.
OL,11,F"It was reflex. The consequences would
OL,12,Fhave been terrible for her ` and for
OL,13,Fme."
OL,15,FIt was reported at the time that 15
OL,16,Fminutes later the jogger appeared on
OL,17,Fthe other side of the bridge, running
OL,18,Fin the opposite direction.
OL,26,@pD@[OUuD@DO]
