CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781556457
OL,3,CMan arrested nine years after
OL,4,Cnotorious 'Putney Pusher' incident
OL,6,FThe victim tried to speak to him but
OL,7,Fhe did not acknowledge her and carried
OL,8,Fon running.
OL,10,FThe runner was described as white,
OL,11,Faged early to mid 30s, with brown eyes
OL,12,Fand short brown hair.
OL,14,FWhile detectives interviewed 50 men
OL,15,Fand arrested three suspects at the
OL,16,Ftime, no one was ever charged.
OL,18,FThe investigation was closed in 2018,
OL,19,Fbut the arrest was made on Monday
OL,20,Fafter new information reportedly came
OL,21,Fto light.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
