PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781556457
OL,3,CMan arrested nine years after
OL,4,Cnotorious 'Putney Pusher' incident
OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "On Monday, 15 June, a 44-year-
OL,8,Fold man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fattempted grievous bodily harm. He was
OL,10,Ftaken to police custody, where he
OL,11,Fremains.
OL,13,F"The arrest relates to an incident on
OL,14,F5 May 2017, where a woman was pushed
OL,15,Finto the path of a bus on Putney
OL,16,FBridge in Putney. Inquiries continue."
